					<p>I think The White Cat would have been better for me if I hadn&#8217;t read this first.  I created ideas about the character and it make it difficult to see him in another light even though he is described as “of a gay and merry disposition.”</p>
<p>It&#8217;s was a bit like reading a piece of fanfiction, deciding what the characters are like and then being disappointed with the original &#8211; how dare the author have their own ideas 😛  </p>
<p>I have to say I do prefer this to the original.</p>
